</P>
<P>
	Lemieux has the largest stake in the team, most of it coming  
from the $25 million in deferred salary the Penguins owed him. 
</P>
<P>
	Lemieux will keep the hockey operation in the hands of general  
manager Craig Patrick while he concentrates on the business side 
